Display component-
    It gets value as input, which are numbers and operations, and returns that with good style

Button component-
    It gets label and onClick as inputs, and returns label which is calculator button, one by one all the buttons, and onClicking of that button, handleClick function defined in
    Calculator component start working to give desired output

Calculator component-
    It returns two components Display, then Button component in map function by iterating all buttons

